      "description": "This E92 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the iconic S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 with individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and aluminum multi-link rear suspension for superior kinematic response. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing inspection and throttle actuator service, ensuring the high-revving internals remain within tight tolerances. While showing honest signs of use consistent with its grade, the mechanical integrity and powertrain calibration remain sharp, offering an visceral, analog driving experience.",
